author: Retro Game Corps
description:
The GPD Win 5 is the first handheld with AMD's Strix Halo CPU, making it the most powerful device in the world.  It's also one of the most expensive handhelds ever.  Let's see what you can expect at the bleeding edge today.

More info: https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/gpd-win-5-the-ultimate-external-battery-handheld/x/18018320#/

This was a review unit sent to me by the manufacturer.  All opinions are my own, they did not see this review ahead of time, and no money was exchanged in any way.
